Ragnus made his way back to the dark avian slower than he would have 
wished.  Long hours were spent fly with the extra burden of 
Perceptor.  Eventually he made it back, transforming into his Robot 
mode before entering the base.  Dragging perceptor behind him, he 
made his way to the command area.
